  "body": "**Is this a BUG REPORT or FEATURE REQUEST?** (choose one): FEATURE REQUEST\r\n\r\nCurrently, there is no easy way to run a flaky e2e test multiple times to reproduce a failure. Node e2e tests apparently expose --ginkgo.untilItFails so that a test can be run many times until it fails. It would be great if the flag is exposed in hack/e2e.go as well.\r\n\r\n@kubernetes/test-infra-maintainers \r\n",
